-radius:0px;border-left-width:3px;border-top-style:none;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;border-bottom-width:3px;border-bottom-style:none;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">新增MySQL配置项</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">在Dify的配置文件中，我们新增了MySQL的配置选项，允许用户指定MySQL数据库的连接信息，包括主机地址、端口、用户名、密码以及数据库名称。这为用户提供了更多选择，使其可以根据自身需求灵活选择数据库类型。</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\">\n      <strong style=\"border-right-style:none;background-size:auto;border-top-width:3px;border-bottom-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background-attachment:scroll;font-weight:bold;padding-left:0px;border-left-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-left:0px;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;border-left-style:none;border-top-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius:0px;margin-top:0px;border-bottom-right-radius:0px;background-image:none;height:auto;padding-top:0px;border-bottom-left-radius:0px;border-right-width:3px;padding-bottom:0px;border-right-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-right-radius:0px;border-left-width:3px;border-top-style:none;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;border-bottom-width:3px;border-bottom-style:none;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">修改数据库和表结构</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">由于PostgreSQL和MySQL在语法和数据类型上存在差异，我们需要对Dify的数据库表结构进行适配性修改。这包括调整字段类型、索引定义以及约束条件等，以确保在MySQL环境下能够正常运行。</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\">\n      <strong style=\"border-right-style:none;background-size:auto;border-top-width:3px;border-bottom-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background-attachment:scroll;font-weight:bold;padding-left:0px;border-left-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-left:0px;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;border-left-style:none;border-top-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius:0px;margin-top:0px;border-bottom-right-radius:0px;background-image:none;height:auto;padding-top:0px;border-bottom-left-radius:0px;border-right-width:3px;padding-bottom:0px;border-right-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-right-radius:0px;border-left-width:3px;border-top-style:none;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;border-bottom-width:3px;border-bottom-style:none;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">SQL语句的适配与修改</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Dify在运行过程中会执行大量的SQL语句，用于数据的增、删、改、查操作。为了兼容MySQL，我们对这些SQL语句进行了逐一审查和修改，确保它们能够在MySQL中正确执行。这一过程需要仔细处理，以避免因语法差异导致的运行错误。</span>\n     </section></li>\n   </ol>\n   <h4 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;\"><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">检索增强</span></span></h4>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/137697b7-8b97-48e2-1297-9c8b6e85fa00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100025291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/137697b7-8b97-48e2-1297-9c8b6e85fa00/public\">\n   </section>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;list-style-type:disc;padding-left:25px;padding-bottom:0px;margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-right:0px;padding-right:0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(58, 58, 58);font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: normal;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">为Dify新增了对Elasticsearch 8的支持，使其能够充分利用Elasticsearch强大的全文检索、聚合分析以及实时数据处理能力。</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(58, 58, 58);font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: normal;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">引入了Contextual Retrieval（上下文检索）功能。通过这一功能，Dify能够在检索时充分考虑查询的上下文背景，从而返回更加符合用户意图的结果。</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(58, 58, 58);font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: normal;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">新增了对GraphRAG（图增强检索）和LightRAG（轻量级检索）的支持。这两种检索方式各有优势，能够为开发者提供更多选择。</span>\n     </section></li>\n   </ul>\n   <h4 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;\"><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">集成内部服务</span></span><span style=\"display: none;\"></span></h4>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bdcfe811-35a5-4160-45cd-bf641b27f200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100025292\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bdcfe811-35a5-4160-45cd-bf641b27f200/public\">\n   </section>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58);line-height: 1.8em;text-indent: 0em;margin: 0px;padding: 8px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 15px;align-items: unset;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: unset;background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position: 0% 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;border-style: none;border-width: 1px;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-radius: 0px;box-shadow: none;display: block;flex-direction: unset;float: unset;height: auto;justify-content: unset;overflow: unset;padding: 0px;text-shadow: none;transform: none;width: auto;-webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;float:unset;border-radius:0px;background-color:unset;box-shadow:none;background-repeat:no-repeat;transform:none;flex-direction:unset;overflow:unset;text-indent:0em;border-width:1px 1px 1px 3px;background-image:none;border-style:none none none solid;height:auto;padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;line-height:1.8em;border-color:rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(255, 177, 27);background-position:0% 0%;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;justify-content:unset;align-items:unset;background-origin:padding-box;-webkit-box-reflect:unset;\"><span leaf=\"\">落地软件机器人 Agent 场景</span></span><span style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58);line-height: 1.8em;text-indent: 0em;margin: 0px;padding: 8px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Dify作为一个强大的AI开发平台，不仅在开发效率上表现出色，更在数据处理、智能问答、业务流程自动化以及SQL生成等场景中展现了强大的能力。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7950a8b2-478c-4523-266a-1a7050f1ed00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100025293\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7950a8b2-478c-4523-266a-1a7050f1ed00/public\">\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d38bc9a8-aec7-45b8-0a90-76f9da283700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100025294\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d38bc9a8-aec7-45b8-0a90-76f9da283700/public\">\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/863ed9b1-8db5-4b1b-8014-64cb25317300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100025295\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/863ed9b1-8db5-4b1b-8014-64cb25317300/public\">\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a9eac00c-43ac-49a4-e297-eaafc4b09700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100025296\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a9eac00c-43ac-49a4-e297-eaafc4b09700/public\">\n   </section>\n   <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 15px;align-items: unset;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: unset;background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position: 0% 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;border-style: none;border-width: 1px;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-radius: 0px;box-shadow: none;display: block;flex-direction: unset;float: unset;height: auto;justify-content: unset;overflow: unset;padding: 0px;text-shadow: none;transform: none;width: auto;-webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;float:unset;border-radius:0px;background-color:unset;box-shadow:none;background-repeat:no-repeat;transform:none;flex-direction:unset;overflow:unset;text-indent:0em;border-width:1px 1px 1px 3px;background-image:none;border-style:none none none solid;height:auto;padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;line-height:1.8em;border-color:rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(255, 177, 27);background-position:0% 0%;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;justify-content:unset;align-items:unset;background-origin:padding-box;-webkit-box-reflect:unset;\"><span leaf=\"\">Dify 实践总结</span></span><span style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58);line-height: 1.8em;text-indent: 0em;margin: 0px;padding: 8px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在未使用Dify平台之前，顺丰的开发流程面临着诸多挑战。开发应用前后端、集成和封装LLM能力需要花费大量时间，尤其是开发前端应用时，往往需要从零开始搭建。然而，引入Dify平台后，开发效率得到了显著提升。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fd72a327-1b44-4824-09d2-bba614be2e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100025297\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fd72a327-1b44-4824-09d2-bba614be2e00/public\">\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e04ecd3e-a0e5-48c8-5892-c0c9e36d9d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100025298\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e04ecd3e-a0e5-48c8-5892-c0c9e36d9d00/public\">\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "顺丰基于 Dify 平台在内部落地 AI Agent 的实践，重点介绍了平台的改造和应用。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "顺丰基于 Dify 平台在内部落地 AI Agent 的实践，重点介绍了平台的改造和应用。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了顺丰公司如何基于 Dify 这一开源 LLM 应用开发平台，在企业内部落地 AI Agent 的实践经验。首先概述了 Dify 的核心功能，如低代码开发、模块化设计、AI 工作流、RAG 管道和 Agent 智能体等。然后，重点介绍了顺丰针对 Dify 平台进行的改造，包括新增 MySQL 配置项以支持更多数据库选择，增强检索能力（支持 Elasticsearch 8、上下文检索、GraphRAG 和 LightRAG），并通过集成内部服务，实现与企业现有系统的无缝对接。最后，阐述了 Dify 在顺丰内部多个场景的应用，如软件机器人 Agent，并总结了 Dify 平台在提升开发效率方面的优势。",
